ram\": \"the country's capital\", \"from\": 1376, \"to\": 1397}, {\"ngram\": \"months\", \"from\": 1403, \"to\": 1409}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The victims were many, the man accused of tormenting them the same: Brij Bhushan Sharan Singh, then a politician from Prime Minister Narendra Modi's ruling Bharatiya Janata Party and the president of the Wrestling Federation of India (WFI).\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1651, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1479, \"end\": 1504, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brij_Bhushan_Sharan_Singh\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Brij Bhushan Sharan Singh\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brij_Bhushan_Sharan_Singh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brij_Bhushan_Sharan_Singh\"}, {\"begin\": 1544, \"end\": 1557, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Narendra Modi\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Narendra_Modi\"}, {\"begin\": 1567, \"end\": 1589, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 0.9999980081354862, \"rank\": 1.9918684511281793e-06, \"text\": \"Bharatiya Janata Party\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The victims\", \"from\": 1411, \"to\": 1422}, {\"ngram\": \"the man\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1441}, {\"ngram\": \"then a politician\", \"from\": 1506, \"to\": 1523}, {\"ngram\": \"the president\", \"from\": 1594, \"to\": 1607}, {\"ngram\": \"the Wrestling Federation\", \"from\": 1611, \"to\": 1635}, {\"ngram\": \"India\", \"from\": 1639, \"to\": 1644}, {\"ngram\": \"WFI\", \"from\": 1646, \"to\": 1649}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet it did not end with the sex