, \"from\": 4305, \"to\": 4323}, {\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 4328, \"to\": 4335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Today, they routinely get threatening calls or offers of large sums of money to dissuade complainants and witnesses from testifying against Singh in court.\", \"from\": 4353, \"to\": 4508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"threatening calls\", \"from\": 4379, \"to\": 4396}, {\"ngram\": \"offers\", \"from\": 4400, \"to\": 4406}, {\"ngram\": \"large sums\", \"from\": 4410, \"to\": 4420}, {\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 4424, \"to\": 4429}, {\"ngram\": \"complainants\", \"from\": 4442, \"to\": 4454}, {\"ngram\": \"witnesses\", \"from\": 4459, \"to\": 4468}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 4493, \"to\": 4498}, {\"ngram\": \"court\", \"from\": 4502, \"to\": 4507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wrestling academies are warned against allowing these wrestlers to train.\", \"from\": 4509, \"to\": 4582, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wrestling academies\", \"from\": 4509, \"to\": 4528}, {\"ngram\": \"these wrestlers\", \"from\": 4557, \"to\": 4572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The child victim has already withdrawn her complaint.\", \"from\": 4584, \"to\": 4637, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The child victim\", \"from\": 4584, \"to\": 4600}, {\"ngram\": \"her complaint\", \"from\": 4623, \"to\": 4636}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those who continue to take on Singh say they fear that the National Anti-Doping Agency (Nada) will be used to destroy their reputation and careers.\", \"from\": 4638, \"to\": 4785, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4726, \"end\": 4730, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RK_Nada_Split\", \"score\": 0.9982788256321098, \"rank\": 0.0006486822173201263, \"text\": \"Nada\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RK_Nada_Split\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RK_Nada_Split\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 4668, \"to\": 4673}, {\"ngram\": \"the National Anti-Doping Agency\", \"from\": 4693, \"to\": 4724}, {\"ngram\": \"their reputation\", \"from\": 4756, \"to\": 4772}, {\"ngram\": \"careers\", \"from\": 4777, \"to\": 4784}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Turning back to look at the road to see if someone had followed him, the man in the SUV recalled an anonymous phone call he received last winter.\", \"from\": 4786, \"to\": 4931, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the road\", \"from\": 4810, \"to\": 4818}, {\"ngram\": \"someone\", \"from\": 4829, \"to\": 4836}, {\"ngram\": \"the man\", \"from\": 4855, \"to\": 4862}, {\"ngram\": \"the SUV\", \"from\": 4866, \"to\": 4873}, {\"ngram\": \"an anonymous phone call\", \"from\": 4883, \"to\": 4906}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The caller said that if the complainant does not back off, 'Dope mein phasa denge' [We will frame her in a doping case],\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 4933, \"to\": 5064, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The caller\", \"from\": 4934, \"to\": 4944}, {\"ngram\": \"the complainant\", \"from\": 4958, \"to\": 4973}, {\"ngram\": \"a doping case\", \"from\": 5039, \"to\": 5052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Soon after, Nada officials arrived at the residential wrestling academy where the complainant stays and practises.\", \"from\": 5066, \"to\": 5180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5078, \"end\": 5082, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RK_Nada_Split\", \"score\": 0.9982788256321098, \"rank\": 0.0006486822173201263, \"text\": \"Nada\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RK_Nada_Split\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RK_Nada_Split\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the residential wrestling academy\", \"from\": 5104, \"to\": 5137}, {\"ngram\": \"the complainant\", \"from\": 5144, \"to\": 5159}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have received orders from the top to conduct your dope test.\", \"from\": 5181, \"to\": 5245, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"orders\", \"from\": 5199, \"to\": 5205}, {\"ngram\": \"the top\", \"from\": 5211, \"to\": 5218}, {\"ngram\": \"your dope test\", \"from\": 5230, \"to\": 5244}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If you do not give [blood and urine] samples, Nada will ban you,\\\" they told her, according to a friend of the female wrestler.\", \"from\": 5246, \"to\": 5372, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5292, \"end\": 5296, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RK_Nada_Split\", \"score\": 0.9982788256321098, \"rank\": 0.0006486822173201263, \"text\": \"Nada\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RK_Nada_Split\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RK_Nada_Split\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"blood\", \"from\": 5266, \"to\": 5271}, {\"ngram\": \"urine\", \"from\": 5276, \"to\": 5281}, {\"ngram\": \"samples\", \"from\": 5283, \"to\": 5290}, {\"ngram\": \"a friend\", \"from\": 5340, \"to\": 5348}, {\"ngram\": \"the female wrestler\", \"from\": 5352, \"to\": 5371}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her guardian corroborated this account.\", \"from\": 5373, \"to\": 5412, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her guardian\", \"from\": 5373, \"to\": 5385}, {\"ngram\": \"this account\", \"from\": 5399, \"to\": 5411}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A few days later she received a notice from Nada.\", \"from\": 5414, \"to\": 5463, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5458, \"end\": 5462, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RK_Nada_Split\", \"score\": 0.9999999900007879, \"rank\": 3.762030205392962e-09, \"text\": \"Nada\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RK_Nada_Split\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RK_Nada_Split\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a notice\", \"from\": 5444, \"to\": 5452}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Traces of a banned substance had been found in her samples.\", \"from\": 5464, \"to\": 5523, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Traces\", \"from\": 5464, \"to\": 5470}, {\"ngram\": \"a banned substance\", \"from\": 5474, \"to\": 5492}, {\"ngram\": \"her samples\", \"from\": 5511, \"to\": 5522}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wrestling is arguably India's most successful Olympic sport today and Haryana is the crucible that churns out the country's champions.\", \"from\": 5525, \"to\": 5659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5547, \"end\": 5552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999999568319717, \"rank\": 4.3069820370501347e-08, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 5595, \"end\": 5602, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8542455521390134e-18, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wrestling\", \"from\": 5525, \"to\": 5534}, {\"ngram\": \"the crucible\", \"from\": 5606, \"to\": 5618}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's champions\", \"from\": 5635, \"to\": 5658}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Of the 21 individual Olympic medals across sports that India has won in 76 years since its independence, six belong to wrestlers from Haryana.\", \"from\": 5661, \"to\": 5803, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5716, \"end\": 5721, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999999568319717, \"rank\": 4.3069820370501347e-08, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 5795, \"end\": 5802, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8542455521390134e-18, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the 21 individual Olympic medals\", \"from\": 5664, \"to\": 5696}, {\"ngram\": \"sports\", \"from\": 5704, \"to\": 5710}, {\"ngram\": \"76 years\", \"from\": 5733, \"to\": 5741}, {\"ngram\": \"its independence\", \"from\": 5748, \"to\": 5764}, {\"ngram\": \"wrestlers\", \"from\": 5780, \"to\": 5789}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The agrarian state that shares its border with Delhi lives mostly in its villages.\", \"from\": 5805, \"to\": 5887, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5852, \"end\": 5857, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"score\": 0.999973085972425, \"rank\": 2.6913608561964274e-05, \"text\": \"Delhi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The agrarian state\", \"from\": 5805, \"to\": 5823}, {\"ngram\": \"its border\", \"from\": 5836, \"to\": 5846}, {\"ngram\": \"its villages\", \"from\": 5874, \"to\": 5886}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It is a deeply patriarchal, conservative society, but also one where, in the late 1990s, young girls grabbed the chance they got to step out of their homes and show their mettle in local tournaments and, eventually, world championships.\", \"from\": 5888, \"to\": 6124, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a deeply patriarchal, conservative society\", \"from\": 5894, \"to\": 5936}, {\"ngram\": \"the late 1990s\", \"from\": 5961, \"to\": 5975}, {\"ngram\": \"young girls\", \"from\": 5977, \"to\": 5988}, {\"ngram\": \"the chance\", \"from\": 5997, \"to\": 6007}, {\"ngram\": \"their homes\", \"from\": 6032, \"to\": 6043}, {\"ngram\": \"their mettle\", \"from\": 6053, \"to\": 6065}, {\"ngram\": \"local tournaments\", \"from\": 6069, \"to\": 6086}]}, {\"sentence\": \"For the Paris Olympics, five women wrestlers - Vinesh Phogat (50kg), Antim Panghal (53kg), Anshu Malik (57kg), Nisha Dahiya (68kg) and Reetika Hooda (76kg) - have qualified from India to compete.\", \"from\": 6126, \"to\": 6321, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6195, \"end\": 6200, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antim_Monastery\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Antim\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antim_Monastery\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Antim_Monastery\"}, {\"begin\": 6217, \"end\": 6228, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anshu_Malik\", \"score\": 0.9999999894841949, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anshu Malik\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anshu_Malik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anshu_Malik\"}, {\"begin\": 6243, \"end\": 6249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dahiya_(surname)\", \"score\": 0.9441587041112357, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Dahiya\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dahiya_(surname)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dahiya_(surname)\"}, {\"begin\": 6304, \"end\": 6309, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9999999568319717, \"rank\": 4.3069820370501347e-08, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 6130, \"to\": 6148}, {\"ngram\": \"five women wrestlers\", \"from\": 6150, \"to\": 6170}, {\"ngram\": \"Vinesh Phogat\", \"from\": 6173, \"to\": 6186}, {\"ngram\": \"50kg\", \"from\": 6188, \"to\": 6192}, {\"ngram\": \"53kg\", \"from\": 6210, \"to\": 6214}, {\"ngram\": \"57kg\", \"from\": 6230, \"to\": 6234}, {\"ngram\": \"68kg\", \"from\": 6251, \"to\": 6255}, {\"ngram\": \"Reetika Hooda\", \"from\": 6261, \"to\": 6274}, {\"ngram\": \"76kg\", \"from\": 6276, \"to\": 6280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All are from Haryana.\", \"from\": 6322, \"to\": 6343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6335, \"end\": 6342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8542455521390134e-18, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The wrestling competition begins on August 5.\", \"from\": 6344, \"to\": 6389, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The wrestling competition\", \"from\": 6344, \"to\": 6369}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 6380, \"to\": 6386}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet even as these women carry the hopes of a nation of 1.4 billion people at the world's greatest sporting extravaganza, fear, more than joy, is palpable in Haryana's wrestling community - from the man in the SUV to the training schools where champions are sculpted.\", \"from\": 6391, \"to\": 6657, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6548, \"end\": 6555, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.8542455521390134e-18, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"these women\", \"from\": 6403, \"to\": 6414}, {\"ngram\": \"the hopes\", \"from\": 6421, \"to\": 6430}, {\"ngram\": \"a nation\", \"from\": 6434, \"to\": 6442}, {\"ngram\": \"1.4 billion people\", \"from\": 6446, \"to\": 6464}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's greatest sporting extravaganza\", \"from\": 6468, \"to\": 6510}, {\"ngram\": \"fear\", \"from\": 6512, \"to\": 6516}, {\"ngram\": \"joy\", \"from\": 6528, \"to\": 6531}, {\"ngram\": \"the man\", \"from\": 6585, \"to\": 6592}, {\"ngram\": \"the SUV\", \"from\": 6596, \"to\": 6603}, {\"ngram\": \"the training schools\", \"from\": 6607, \"to\": 6627}, {\"ngram\": \"champions\", \"from\": 6634, \"to\": 6643}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A year and a half after the protests, Singh is now on trial for sexual harassment and is no longer a politician or the chief of WFI.\", \"from\": 6659, \"to\": 6791, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the protests\", \"from\": 6683, \"to\": 6695}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 6697, \"to\": 6702}, {\"ngram\": \"trial\", \"from\": 6713, \"to\": 6718}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual harassment\", \"from\": 6723, \"to\": 6740}, {\"ngram\": \"a politician\", \"from\": 6758, \"to\": 6770}, {\"ngram\": \"the chief\", \"from\": 6774, \"to\": 6783}, {\"ngram\": \"WFI\", \"from\": 6787, \"to\": 6790}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In January last year, the sports ministry had asked Singh to \\\"step aside\\\" as WFI chief so that the allegations against him could be investigated.\", \"from\": 6792, \"to\": 6937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6818, \"end\": 6833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_ministry\", \"score\": 0.999999999020929, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"sports ministry\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_ministry\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sports_ministry\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 6795, \"to\": 6802}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 6844, \"to\": 6849}, {\"ngram\": \"WFI chief\", \"from\": 6869, \"to\": 6878}, {\"ngram\": \"the allegations\", \"from\": 6887, \"to\": 6902}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But his close ties to the BJP's top leaders remain intact, and he has placed his confidants in key positions in the WFI, allowing him to run the federation by proxy, wrestlers and coaches told Al Jazeera.\", \"from\": 6939, \"to\": 7143, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6965, \"end\": 6968, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 0.9999999758337029, \"rank\": 2.0889579168334277e-08, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}, {\"begin\": 7132, \"end\": 7142, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 0.999966214931553, \"rank\": 2.911263181408983e-05, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbp