": 7762, \"to\": 7782}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But now, says Amarjeet Nehra, who runs a wrestling academy in Rohtak, parents are reluctant to put their daughters in a game that's acquired a \\\"bad reputation\\\".\", \"from\": 7785, \"to\": 7945, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7808, \"end\": 7813, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashish_Nehra\", \"score\": 0.9999988972802325, \"rank\": 1.1027130017279025e-06, \"text\": \"Nehra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashish_Nehra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ashish_Nehra\"}, {\"begin\": 7847, \"end\": 7853, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohtak\", \"score\": 0.9998128824482727, \"rank\": 0.00018715111859600775, \"text\": \"Rohtak\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohtak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohtak\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a wrestling academy\", \"from\": 7824, \"to\": 7843}, {\"ngram\": \"parents\", \"from\": 7855, \"to\": 7862}, {\"ngram\": \"their daughters\", \"from\": 7884, \"to\": 7899}, {\"ngram\": \"a game\", \"from\": 7903, \"to\": 7909}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"bad reputation\", \"from\": 7926, \"to\": 7943}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are scared [that] their girls will be sexually abused,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 7946, \"to\": 8016, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their girls\", \"from\": 7970, \"to\": 7981}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Rohtak has more than a dozen wrestling academies and there is been a drop in attendance at all.\", \"from\": 8017, \"to\": 8112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8017, \"end\": 8023, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohtak\", \"score\": 0.9998128824482727, \"rank\": 0.00018715111859600775, \"text\": \"Rohtak\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohtak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohtak\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more than a 