 \"to\": 12577, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"mayhem\", \"from\": 12570, \"to\": 12576}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They [Singh's men] will murder you',\\\" Malik, who is tall, muscular and looks freakishly fit, said.\", \"from\": 12578, \"to\": 12676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12616, \"end\": 12621, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malik\", \"score\": 0.9999836432138733, \"rank\": 1.5867371897548685e-05, \"text\": \"Malik\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malik\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Singh's men\", \"from\": 12584, \"to\": 12595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He left the camp that day.\", \"from\": 12678, \"to\": 12704, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the camp\", \"from\": 12686, \"to\": 12694}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nearly a decade later, Malik's unheeded warning about the dark and dirty underbelly of Indian wrestling would return to haunt the country.\", \"from\": 12705, \"to\": 12843, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 12728, \"end\": 12733, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malik\", \"score\": 0.9999836432138733, \"rank\": 1.5867371897548685e-05, \"text\": \"Malik\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malik\"}, {\"begin\": 12792, \"end\": 12808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pehlwani\", \"score\": 0.9999999773689299, \"rank\": 2.2631105806903398e-08, \"text\": \"Indian wrestling\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pehlwani\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pehlwani\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dark and dirty underbelly\", \"from\": 12759, \"to\": 12788}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 12831, \"to\": 12842}]}, {\"sentence\": \"About 170km (105 miles) from Delhi, in Haryana's sleepy Sasai village, women, their faces veiled with thin scarves, balance bales of hay on their heads and walk past a small pond where