ngram\": \"his wrestling daughters\", \"from\": 17686, \"to\": 17709}, {\"ngram\": \"superstar\", \"from\": 17720, \"to\": 17729}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Phogat sisters became famous, women wrestlers became national icons and were being celebrated - honoured with cash prizes and high-profile jobs.\", \"from\": 17791, \"to\": 17939, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 17795, \"end\": 17809, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Phogat sisters\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Phogat_sisters\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"women wrestlers\", \"from\": 17825, \"to\": 17840}, {\"ngram\": \"national icons\", \"from\": 17848, \"to\": 17862}, {\"ngram\": \"cash prizes\", \"from\": 17905, \"to\": 17916}, {\"ngram\": \"high-profile jobs\", \"from\": 17921, \"to\": 17938}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Parents would watch Dangal at night, dream that their daughters will become Geeta and Babita (another one of Mahavir's daughters), and would come here in the morning,\\\" Sanjay said.\", \"from\": 17941, \"to\": 18122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18028, \"end\": 18034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babita_Kumari\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.999984984110517e-32, \"text\": \"Babita\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babita_Kumari\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Babita_Kumari\"}, {\"begin\": 18051, \"end\": 18058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mahavira\", \"score\": 0.9999999999993179, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mahavir\", \"types\": [\"Q24229398\", \"Q178885\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mahavira\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mahavira\"}, {\"begin\": 18110, \"end\": 18116, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanjay_Kapoor\", \"score\": 0.8989647206524033, \"rank\": 0.11239070369759935, \"text\": \"Sanjay\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanjay_Kapoor\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanjay_Kapoor\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Parents\", \"from\": 17942, \"to\": 17949}, {\"ngram\": \"Dangal\", \"from\": 17962, \"to\": 17968}, {\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 17972, \"to\": 17977}, {\"ngram\": \"their daughters\", \"from\": 17990, \"to\": 18005}, {\"ngram\": \"Geeta\", \"from\": 18018, \"to\": 18023}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 18096, \"to\": 18107}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, in January last year, stories of sexual abuse by Singh barrelled through the villages, homes and wrestling academies of Haryana, leaving a trail of anger, confusion and fear in their wake.\", \"from\": 18124, \"to\": 18318, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18250, \"end\": 18257, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 8.464564822247739e-16, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 18133, \"to\": 18140}, {\"ngram\": \"stories\", \"from\": 18152, \"to\": 18159}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual abuse\", \"from\": 18163, \"to\": 18175}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 18179, \"to\": 18184}, {\"ngram\": \"the villages\", \"from\": 18203, \"to\": 18215}, {\"ngram\": \"homes\", \"from\": 18217, \"to\": 18222}, {\"ngram\": \"wrestling academies\", \"from\": 18227, \"to\": 18246}, {\"ngram\": \"a trail\", \"from\": 18267, \"to\": 18274}, {\"ngram\": \"anger\", \"from\": 18278, \"to\": 18283}, {\"ngram\": \"confusion\", \"from\": 18285, \"to\": 18294}, {\"ngram\": \"fear\", \"from\": 18299, \"to\": 18303}, {\"ngram\": \"their wake\", \"from\": 18307, \"to\": 18317}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But there was also hope.\", \"from\": 18320, \"to\": 18344, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"hope\", \"from\": 18339, \"to\": 18343}]}, {\"sentence\": \"World champions, Olympians, were on the streets protesting.\", \"from\": 18345, \"to\": 18404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"World champions\", \"from\": 18345, \"to\": 18360}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 18362, \"to\": 18371}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 18381, \"to\": 18392}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Surely, many thought, the government would step in and clean up the WFI.\", \"from\": 18405, \"to\": 18477, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 18427, \"to\": 18441}, {\"ngram\": \"the WFI\", \"from\": 18469, \"to\": 18476}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Last year, as Delhi shivered in its coldest January in more than a decade, wrestlers braved the chill and sat huddled together in puffer jackets and thick sweaters on thin mattresses on a pavement.\", \"from\": 18479, \"to\": 18676, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18493, \"end\": 18498, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"score\": 0.9999994182246028, \"rank\": 4.87737550469535e-07, \"text\": \"Delhi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its coldest January\", \"from\": 18511, \"to\": 18530}, {\"ngram\": \"more than a decade\", \"from\": 18534, \"to\": 18552}, {\"ngram\": \"wrestlers\", \"from\": 18554, \"to\": 18563}, {\"ngram\": \"the chill\", \"from\": 18571, \"to\": 18580}, {\"ngram\": \"puffer jackets\", \"from\": 18609, \"to\": 18623}, {\"ngram\": \"thick sweaters\", \"from\": 18628, \"to\": 18642}, {\"ngram\": \"thin mattresses\", \"from\": 18646, \"to\": 18661}, {\"ngram\": \"a pavement\", \"from\": 18665, \"to\": 18675}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One of them was Anshu Malik, 22, a rising star on the international wrestling circuit.\", \"from\": 18677, \"to\": 18763, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18693, \"end\": 18704, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anshu_Malik\", \"score\": 0.9999999894843086, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anshu Malik\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anshu_Malik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anshu_Malik\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rising star\", \"from\": 18710, \"to\": 18723}, {\"ngram\": \"the international wrestling circuit\", \"from\": 18727, \"to\": 18762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the second day of the protest, Malik, a formidable grappler in the 57kg weight category, took the mic to share how Singh would often behave during international tours.\", \"from\": 18765, \"to\": 18935, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 18799, \"end\": 18804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malik\", \"score\": 0.9999856469787627, \"rank\": 1.397845246828476e-05, \"text\": \"Malik\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malik\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the second day\", \"from\": 18768, \"to\": 18782}, {\"ngram\": \"the protest\", \"from\": 18786, \"to\": 18797}, {\"ngram\": \"a formidable grappler\", \"from\": 18806, \"to\": 18827}, {\"ngram\": \"the 57kg weight category\", \"from\": 18831, \"to\": 18855}, {\"ngram\": \"the mic\", \"from\": 18862, \"to\": 18869}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 18883, \"to\": 18888}, {\"ngram\": \"international tours\", \"from\": 18915, \"to\": 18934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wearing an olive green sweatshirt over blue-and-white printed slacks, she stood next to Punia and said Singh, in a brazen violation of rules, would not only stay in the same hotel as women wrestlers, but would \\\"take an adjacent room and keep his door open\\\".\", \"from\": 18936, \"to\": 19193, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19024, \"end\": 19029, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajrang_Punia\", \"score\": 0.9999997317440052, \"rank\": 2.682502712787697e-07, \"text\": \"Punia\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajrang_Punia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bajrang_Punia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an olive green sweatshirt\", \"from\": 18944, \"to\": 18969}, {\"ngram\": \"blue-and-white printed slacks\", \"from\": 18975, \"to\": 19004}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 19039, \"to\": 19044}, {\"ngram\": \"a brazen violation\", \"from\": 19049, \"to\": 19067}, {\"ngram\": \"rules\", \"from\": 19071, \"to\": 19076}, {\"ngram\": \"the same hotel\", \"from\": 19101, \"to\": 19115}, {\"ngram\": \"women wrestlers\", \"from\": 19119, \"to\": 19134}, {\"ngram\": \"an adjacent room\", \"from\": 19152, \"to\": 19168}, {\"ngram\": \"his door\", \"from\": 19178, \"to\": 19186}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Singh had a reputation of lifting the shirts of women wrestlers in public and groping them on the pretext of checking their breathing.\", \"from\": 19195, \"to\": 19329, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 19195, \"to\": 19200}, {\"ngram\": \"a reputation\", \"from\": 19205, \"to\": 19217}, {\"ngram\": \"the shirts\", \"from\": 19229, \"to\": 19239}, {\"ngram\": \"women wrestlers\", \"from\": 19243, \"to\": 19258}, {\"ngram\": \"public\", \"from\": 19262, \"to\": 19268}, {\"ngram\": \"the pretext\", \"from\": 19289, \"to\": 19300}, {\"ngram\": \"their breathing\", \"from\": 19313, \"to\": 19328}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His constant presence around their rooms during tournaments was creepy, stifling and threw them off their game, Malik said.\", \"from\": 19330, \"to\": 19453, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19442, \"end\": 19447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malik\", \"score\": 0.9999856469787627, \"rank\": 1.397845246828476e-05, \"text\": \"Malik\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Malik\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His constant presence\", \"from\": 19330, \"to\": 19351}, {\"ngram\": \"their rooms\", \"from\": 19359, \"to\": 19370}, {\"ngram\": \"tournaments\", \"from\": 19378, \"to\": 19389}, {\"ngram\": \"their game\", \"from\": 19430, \"to\": 19440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If players are uncomfortable in their own rooms, how will they compete?\\\"\", \"from\": 19455, \"to\": 19528, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 19459, \"to\": 19466}, {\"ngram\": \"their own rooms\", \"from\": 19488, \"to\": 19503}]}, {\"sentence\": \"she asked, her voice earnest and resolute.\", \"from\": 19529, \"to\": 19571, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her voice\", \"from\": 19540, \"to\": 19549}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During his tenure as WFI president, Singh, riding on the success of wrestlers from Haryana, raised the federation's profile.\", \"from\": 19573, \"to\": 19697, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 19656, \"end\": 19663, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 0.9999994758434477, \"rank\": 4.332470708242678e-07, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his tenure\", \"from\": 19580, \"to\": 19590}, {\"ngram\": \"WFI president\", \"from\": 19594, \"to\": 19607}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 19609, \"to\": 19614}, {\"ngram\": \"the success\", \"from\": 19626, \"to\": 19637}, {\"ngram\": \"wrestlers\", \"from\": 19641, \"to\": 19650}, {\"ngram\": \"the federation's profile\", \"from\": 19672, \"to\": 19696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He improved facilities, streamlined the annual tournament calendar, increased the number of competitions and introduced open ranking tournaments that allowed wrestlers from across the country to compete with the best in their weight category.\", \"from\": 19698, \"to\": 19940, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"facilities\", \"from\": 19710, \"to\": 19720}, {\"ngram\": \"the annual tournament calendar\", \"from\": 19734, \"to\": 19764}, {\"ngram\": \"the number\", \"from\": 19776, \"to\": 19786}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 19790, \"to\": 19802}, {\"ngram\": \"open ranking tournaments\", \"from\": 19818, \"to\": 19842}, {\"ngram\": \"wrestlers\", \"from\": 19856, \"to\": 19865}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 19878, \"to\": 19889}, {\"ngram\": \"their weight category\", \"from\": 19918, \"to\": 19939}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also used his political clout to bring in corporate sponsors to give out prizes, cash awards and even stipends to wrestlers.\", \"from\": 19941, \"to\": 20068, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his political clout\", \"from\": 19954, \"to\": 19973}, {\"ngram\": \"corporate sponsors\", \"from\": 19986, \"to\": 20004}, {\"ngram\": \"prizes\", \"from\": 20017, \"to\": 20023}, {\"ngram\": \"cash awards\", \"from\": 20025, \"to\": 20036}, {\"ngram\": \"even stipends\", \"from\": 20041, \"to\": 20054}, {\"ngram\": \"wrestlers\", \"from\": 20058, \"to\": 20067}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His supporters say that he brought in discipline and put a check on top wrestlers misusing privileges.\", \"from\": 20069, \"to\": 20171, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His supporters\", \"from\": 20069, \"to\": 20083}, {\"ngram\": \"discipline\", \"from\": 20107, \"to\": 20117}, {\"ngram\": \"a check\", \"from\": 20126, \"to\": 20133}, {\"ngram\": \"top wrestlers misusing privileges\", \"from\": 20137, \"to\": 20170}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But he also ran WFI like his personal fiefdom, say his critics.\", \"from\": 20173, \"to\": 20236, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"WFI\", \"from\": 20189, \"to\": 20192}, {\"ngram\": \"his personal fiefdom\", \"from\": 20198, \"to\": 20218}, {\"ngram\": \"his critics\", \"from\": 20224, \"to\": 20235}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Apart from holding the post of WFI president, Singh was the chair of the WFI's grievance redressal committee, which meant that all sexual harassment complaints would land at his desk.\", \"from\": 20237, \"to\": 20420, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the post\", \"from\": 20256, \"to\": 20264}, {\"ngram\": \"WFI president\", \"from\": 20268, \"to\": 20281}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 20283, \"to\": 20288}, {\"ngram\": \"the chair\", \"from\": 20293, \"to\": 20302}, {\"ngram\": \"the WFI's grievance redressal committee\", \"from\": 20306, \"to\": 20345}, {\"ngram\": \"all sexual harassment complaints\", \"from\": 20364, \"to\": 20396}, {\"ngram\": \"his desk\", \"from\": 20411, \"to\": 20419}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He also headed WFI's selection committee, which recommended the wrestlers who would represent the country in international tournaments, and so held power over careers.\", \"from\": 20421, \"to\": 20588, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"WFI's selection committee\", \"from\": 20436, \"to\": 20461}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrestlers\", \"from\": 20481, \"to\": 20494}, {\"ngram\": \"the country\", \"from\": 20515, \"to\": 20526}, {\"ngram\": \"international tournaments\", \"from\": 20530, \"to\": 20555}, {\"ngram\": \"so held power\", \"from\": 20561, \"to\": 20574}, {\"ngram\": \"careers\", \"from\": 20580, \"to\": 20587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Singh was also the president of Uttar Pradesh's wrestling association.\", \"from\": 20589, \"to\": 20659, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 20621, \"end\": 20634, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uttar_Pradesh\", \"score\": 0.9999951746454376, \"rank\": 2.4980275808695765e-06, \"text\": \"Uttar Pradesh\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uttar_Pradesh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uttar_Pradesh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 20589, \"to\": 20594}, {\"ngram\": \"the president\", \"from\": 20604, \"to\": 20617}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Unlike tennis and other sports where athletes can compete as individuals in tournaments, in international wrestling tournaments, grapplers can only compete as part of a national team.\", \"from\": 20661, \"to\": 20844, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tennis\", \"from\": 20668, \"to\": 20674}, {\"ngram\": \"other sports\", \"from\": 20679, \"to\": 20691}, {\"ngram\": \"athletes\", \"from\": 20698, \"to\": 20706}, {\"ngram\": \"individuals\", \"from\": 20722, \"to\": 20733}, {\"ngram\": \"tournaments\", \"from\": 20737, \"to\": 20748}, {\"ngram\": \"international wrestling tournaments\", \"from\": 20753, \"to\": 20788}, {\"ngram\": \"grapplers\", \"from\": 20790, \"to\": 20799}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 20820, \"to\": 20824}, {\"ngram\": \"a national team\", \"from\": 20828, \"to\": 20843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"He kept the referees under his control.\", \"from\": 20846, \"to\": 20886, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the referees\", \"from\": 20855, \"to\": 20867}, {\"ngram\": \"his control\", \"from\": 20874, \"to\": 20885}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So scared were they that whatever he would say, they would repeat like parrots and give the decisions that he wanted,\\\" Geeta Phogat told Al Jazeera last year.\", \"from\": 20887, \"to\": 21045, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 21024, \"end\": 21034, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 0.9998417205531694, \"rank\": 0.00015625623007663175, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 20912, \"to\": 20920}, {\"ngram\": \"parrots\", \"from\": 20958, \"to\": 20965}, {\"ngram\": \"the decisions\", \"from\": 20975, \"to\": 20988}, {\"ngram\": \"Geeta Phogat\", \"from\": 21006, \"to\": 21018}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Those who kowtowed to him, he would give them facilities, send them on foreign tours, make them coaches, physiotherapists.\", \"from\": 21047, \"to\": 21170, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"facilities\", \"from\": 21094, \"to\": 21104}, {\"ngram\": \"foreign tours\", \"from\": 21119, \"to\": 21132}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There were so many things we tolerated, so many things we saw, but kept quiet,\\\" she said, because of the fear that he would destroy their careers.\", \"from\": 21171, \"to\": 21317, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so many things\", \"from\": 21182, \"to\": 21196}, {\"ngram\": \"so many things\", \"from\": 21211, \"to\": 21225}, {\"ngram\": \"the fear\", \"from\": 21272, \"to\": 21280}, {\"ngram\": \"their careers\", \"from\": 21303, \"to\": 21316}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2023, WFI elections were due.\", \"from\": 21319, \"to\": 21351, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"WFI elections\", \"from\": 21328, \"to\": 21341}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Singh, who had hit the three-term limit as president, was no longer eligible.\", \"from\": 21352, \"to\": 21429, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 21352, \"to\": 21357}, {\"ngram\": \"the three-term limit\", \"from\": 21371, \"to\": 21391}, {\"ngram\": \"president\", \"from\": 21395, \"to\": 21404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But in his 12 years as president, he had placed family members and loyalists in key positions in the WFI and the 20-plus state wrestling associations.\", \"from\": 21430, \"to\": 21580, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his 12 years\", \"from\": 21437, \"to\": 21449}, {\"ngram\": \"president\", \"from\": 21453, \"to\": 21462}, {\"ngram\": \"family members\", \"from\": 21478, \"to\": 21492}, {\"ngram\": \"loyalists\", \"from\": 21497, \"to\": 21506}, {\"ngram\": \"key positions\", \"from\": 21510, \"to\": 21523}, {\"ngram\": \"the WFI\", \"from\": 21527, \"to\": 21534}, {\"ngram\": \"the 20-plus state wrestling associations\", \"from\": 21539, \"to\": 21579}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The wrestlers feared he would get them elected so he could continue to run the WFI by proxy.\", \"from\": 21582, \"to\": 21674, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The wrestlers\", \"from\": 21582, \"to\": 21595}, {\"ngram\": \"the WFI\", \"from\": 21657, \"to\": 21664}, {\"ngram\": \"proxy\", \"from\": 21668, \"to\": 21673}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If his reign continued, they worried, so, too, would the sexual abuse.\", \"from\": 21675, \"to\": 21745, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his reign\", \"from\": 21678, \"to\": 21687}, {\"ngram\": \"the sexual abuse\", \"from\": 21728, \"to\": 21744}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The January protest ended after three days, following assurances from the government that justice would be done.\", \"from\": 21747, \"to\": 21859, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The January protest\", \"from\": 21747, \"to\": 21766}, {\"ngram\": \"three days\", \"from\": 21779, \"to\": 21789}, {\"ngram\": \"assurances\", \"from\": 21801, \"to\": 21811}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 21817, \"to\": 21831}, {\"ngram\": \"justice\", \"from\": 21837, \"to\": 21844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Singh was asked to step down and committees were appointed to inquire into the wrestlers' allegations and to run the WFI in the interim.\", \"from\": 21860, \"to\": 21996, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 21860, \"to\": 21865}, {\"ngram\": \"committees\", \"from\": 21893, \"to\": 21903}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrestlers' allegations\", \"from\": 21935, \"to\": 21961}, {\"ngram\": \"the WFI\", \"from\": 21973, \"to\": 21980}, {\"ngram\": \"the interim\", \"from\": 21984, \"to\": 21995}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The wrestlers were deposed and the inquiry report was submitted, but its findings were not made public.\", \"from\": 21998, \"to\": 22101, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The wrestlers\", \"from\": 21998, \"to\": 22011}, {\"ngram\": \"the inquiry report\", \"from\": 22029, \"to\": 22047}, {\"ngram\": \"its findings\", \"from\": 22067, \"to\": 22079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The government remained silent on Singh and charges of sexual harassment.\", \"from\": 22102, \"to\": 22175, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The government\", \"from\": 22102, \"to\": 22116}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 22136, \"to\": 22141}, {\"ngram\": \"charges\", \"from\": 22146, \"to\": 22153}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual harassment\", \"from\": 22157, \"to\": 22174}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Instead, WFI elections were announced.\", \"from\": 22177, \"to\": 22215, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"WFI elections\", \"from\": 22186, \"to\": 22199}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Singh looked all set to regain control of WFI, so the wrestlers returned to the streets in April, this time for a much longer and challenging haul.\", \"from\": 22217, \"to\": 22364, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 22217, \"to\": 22222}, {\"ngram\": \"control\", \"from\": 22248, \"to\": 22255}, {\"ngram\": \"WFI\", \"from\": 22259, \"to\": 22262}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrestlers\", \"from\": 22267, \"to\": 22280}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 22293, \"to\": 22304}, {\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 22308, \"to\": 22313}, {\"ngram\": \"a much longer and challenging haul\", \"from\": 22329, \"to\": 22363}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's when seven wrestlers, including a minor, filed police complaints against Singh, and began their sit-in protest in peak summer on a pavement in the heart of Delhi's busy Connaught Place, next to Jantar Mantar, an 18th-century observatory.\", \"from\": 22365, \"to\": 22609, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22528, \"end\": 22533, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"score\": 0.9997100978270808, \"rank\": 0.00023583666304415908, \"text\": \"Delhi\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi\"}, {\"begin\": 22541, \"end\": 22556, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connaught_Place,_New_Delhi\", \"score\": 0.9857420488125324, \"rank\": 0.010519395134779438, \"text\": \"Connaught Place\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connaught_Place,_New_Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Connaught_Place,_New_Delhi\"}, {\"begin\": 22566, \"end\": 22579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jantar_Mantar\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.5028887143407687e-25, \"text\": \"Jantar Mantar\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jantar_Mantar\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jantar_Mantar\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"seven wrestlers\", \"from\": 22377, \"to\": 22392}, {\"ngram\": \"police complaints\", \"from\": 22419, \"to\": 22436}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 22445, \"to\": 22450}, {\"ngram\": \"their sit-in protest\", \"from\": 22462, \"to\": 22482}, {\"ngram\": \"peak summer\", \"from\": 22486, \"to\": 22497}, {\"ngram\": \"a pavement\", \"from\": 22501, \"to\": 22511}, {\"ngram\": \"the heart\", \"from\": 22515, \"to\": 22524}, {\"ngram\": \"an 18th-century observatory\", \"from\": 22581, \"to\": 22608}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They demanded Singh's arrest based on their complaints, but the police registered a First Information Report - the first step towards an investigation - only after it was directed by the Supreme Court to do so.\", \"from\": 22611, \"to\": 22821, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 22798, \"end\": 22811, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Supreme_Court_of_India\", \"score\": 0.9999998178644939, \"rank\": 1.7933802022445964e-07, \"text\": \"Supreme Court\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Supreme_Court_of_India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Supreme_Court_of_India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Singh's arrest\", \"from\": 22625, \"to\": 22639}, {\"ngram\": \"their complaints\", \"from\": 22649, \"to\": 22665}, {\"ngram\": \"the police\", \"from\": 22671, \"to\": 22681}, {\"ngram\": \"a First Information Report\", \"from\": 22693, \"to\": 22719}, {\"ngram\": \"the first step\", \"from\": 22722, \"to\": 22736}, {\"ngram\": \"an investigation\", \"from\": 22745, \"to\": 22761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The administration and the police, which were passive earlier, turned openly hostile throughout the 46 days when the country's top athletes lived, ate and slept on the pavement.\", \"from\": 22823, \"to\": 23000, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The administration\", \"from\": 22823, \"to\": 22841}, {\"ngram\": \"the police\", \"from\": 22846, \"to\": 22856}, {\"ngram\": \"the 46 days\", \"from\": 22919, \"to\": 22930}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's top athletes\", \"from\": 22936, \"to\": 22962}, {\"ngram\": \"the pavement\", \"from\": 22987, \"to\": 22999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On their left, at a distance of about 2km (1.2 miles), was the parliament.\", \"from\": 23002, \"to\": 23076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their left\", \"from\": 23005, \"to\": 23015}, {\"ngram\": \"a distance\", \"from\": 23020, \"to\": 23030}, {\"ngram\": \"about 2km\", \"from\": 23034, \"to\": 23043}, {\"ngram\": \"1.2 miles\", \"from\": 23045, \"to\": 23054}, {\"ngram\": \"the parliament\", \"from\": 23061, \"to\": 23075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If the protesting wrestlers walked for two minutes to their right, they'd reach the gates of Singh's official bungalow, which was also the WFI's office then, the site of several instances of sexual abuse.\", \"from\": 23077, \"to\": 23281, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the protesting wrestlers\", \"from\": 23080, \"to\": 23104}, {\"ngram\": \"two minutes\", \"from\": 23116, \"to\": 23127}, {\"ngram\": \"their right\", \"from\": 23131, \"to\": 23142}, {\"ngram\": \"the gates\", \"from\": 23157, \"to\": 23166}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh's official bungalow\", \"from\": 23170, \"to\": 23195}, {\"ngram\": \"the WFI's office\", \"from\": 23212, \"to\": 23228}, {\"ngram\": \"the site\", \"from\": 23235, \"to\": 23243}, {\"ngram\": \"several instances\", \"from\": 23247, \"to\": 23264}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual abuse\", \"from\": 23268, \"to\": 23280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the wrestlers were hemmed in on both sides by barricades, checkpoints with metal detectors and a strong police force, so they turned their small patch of footpath into a lively theatre of dissent.\", \"from\": 23283, \"to\": 23483, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wrestlers\", \"from\": 23287, \"to\": 23300}, {\"ngram\": \"both sides\", \"from\": 23319, \"to\": 23329}, {\"ngram\": \"barricades\", \"from\": 23333, \"to\": 23343}, {\"ngram\": \"checkpoints\", \"from\": 23345, \"to\": 23356}, {\"ngram\": \"metal detectors\", \"from\": 23362, \"to\": 23377}, {\"ngram\": \"a strong police force\", \"from\": 23382, \"to\": 23403}, {\"ngram\": \"their small patch\", \"from\": 23420, \"to\": 23437}, {\"ngram\": \"footpath\", \"from\": 23441, \"to\": 23449}, {\"ngram\": \"a lively theatre\", \"from\": 23455, \"to\": 23471}, {\"ngram\": \"dissent\", \"from\": 23475, \"to\": 23482}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Posters with photos of Singh standing behind bars and white plex sheets with details of his criminal cases dangled from trees.\", \"from\": 23484, \"to\": 23610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Posters\", \"from\": 23484, \"to\": 23491}, {\"ngram\": \"photos\", \"from\": 23497, \"to\": 23503}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 23507, \"to\": 23512}, {\"ngram\": \"bars\", \"from\": 23529, \"to\": 23533}, {\"ngram\": \"white plex sheets\", \"from\": 23538, \"to\": 23555}, {\"ngram\": \"details\", \"from\": 23561, \"to\": 23568}, {\"ngram\": \"his criminal cases\", \"from\": 23572, \"to\": 23590}, {\"ngram\": \"trees\", \"from\": 23604, \"to\": 23609}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A tarp over the protest site offered shade, and two tall pedestal fans whirred on either side of their shanty.\", \"from\": 23612, \"to\": 23722, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A tarp\", \"from\": 23612, \"to\": 23618}, {\"ngram\": \"the protest site\", \"from\": 23624, \"to\": 23640}, {\"ngram\": \"shade\", \"from\": 23649, \"to\": 23654}, {\"ngram\": \"two tall pedestal fans\", \"from\": 23660, \"to\": 23682}, {\"ngram\": \"either side\", \"from\": 23694, \"to\": 23705}, {\"ngram\": \"their shanty\", \"from\": 23709, \"to\": 23721}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Electricity to the protest site would be cut off often.\", \"from\": 23723, \"to\": 23778, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Electricity\", \"from\": 23723, \"to\": 23734}, {\"ngram\": \"the protest site\", \"from\": 23738, \"to\": 23754}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So at night, triangular mosquito nets would pop up, and wrestlers would huddle inside them.\", \"from\": 23779, \"to\": 23870, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"night\", \"from\": 23785, \"to\": 23790}, {\"ngram\": \"triangular mosquito nets\", \"from\": 23792, \"to\": 23816}, {\"ngram\": \"wrestlers\", \"from\": 23835, \"to\": 23844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"About two weeks into the protest, when Haryana's farmers tried to join the wrestler's protest, barricades were set up by Delhi Police at the capital's border to stop them.\", \"from\": 23872, \"to\": 24043, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 23911, \"end\": 23918, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999997726, \"rank\": 1.7575308068938273e-13, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}, {\"begin\": 23993, \"end\": 24005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi_Police\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Delhi Police\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi_Police\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Delhi_Police\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the protest\", \"from\": 23893, \"to\": 23904}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrestler's protest\", \"from\": 23943, \"to\": 23965}, {\"ngram\": \"barricades\", \"from\": 23967, \"to\": 23977}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital's border\", \"from\": 24009, \"to\": 24029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On May 28 last year, when the wrestlers tried to march to the new parliament building on its inauguration day, to register their objection to Singh's presence at the ceremony as a sitting MP, they were manhandled and dragged across the streets by the police.\", \"from\": 24045, \"to\": 24303, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 24048, \"to\": 24051}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrestlers\", \"from\": 24071, \"to\": 24084}, {\"ngram\": \"the new parliament building\", \"from\": 24103, \"to\": 24130}, {\"ngram\": \"its inauguration day\", \"from\": 24134, \"to\": 24154}, {\"ngram\": \"their objection\", \"from\": 24168, \"to\": 24183}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh's presence\", \"from\": 24187, \"to\": 24203}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 24207, \"to\": 24219}, {\"ngram\": \"a sitting MP\", \"from\": 24223, \"to\": 24235}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 24277, \"to\": 24288}, {\"ngram\": \"the police\", \"from\": 24292, \"to\": 24302}]}, {\"sentence\": \"When the wrestlers still refused to budge despite all this, a chorus of lesser-known wrestlers rose in defence of Singh.\", \"from\": 24305, \"to\": 24425, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the wrestlers\", \"from\": 24310, \"to\": 24323}, {\"ngram\": \"a chorus\", \"from\": 24365, \"to\": 24373}, {\"ngram\": \"lesser-known wrestlers\", \"from\": 24377, \"to\": 24399}, {\"ngram\": \"defence\", \"from\": 24408, \"to\": 24415}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 24419, \"to\": 24424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They called the protest a coup of sorts, an attempt by senior players whose careers were over to take over the WFI.\", \"from\": 24426, \"to\": 24541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the protest\", \"from\": 24438, \"to\": 24449}, {\"ngram\": \"a coup\", \"from\": 24450, \"to\": 24456}, {\"ngram\": \"sorts\", \"from\": 24460, \"to\": 24465}, {\"ngram\": \"an attempt\", \"from\": 24467, \"to\": 24477}, {\"ngram\": \"senior players\", \"from\": 24481, \"to\": 24495}, {\"ngram\": \"whose careers\", \"from\": 24496, \"to\": 24509}, {\"ngram\": \"the WFI\", \"from\": 24533, \"to\": 24540}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They claimed that the allegations against Singh were \\\"fake\\\" because they had themselves not seen or suffered sexual abuse.\", \"from\": 24542, \"to\": 24664, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the allegations\", \"from\": 24560, \"to\": 24575}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 24584, \"to\": 24589}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual abuse\", \"from\": 24651, \"to\": 24663}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The day Brij Bhushan does not have the backing of the government at the centre, many more girls will come forward and complain about him,\\\" Vinesh Phogat said.\", \"from\": 24666, \"to\": 24825, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Brij Bhushan\", \"from\": 24675, \"to\": 24687}, {\"ngram\": \"the backing\", \"from\": 24702, \"to\": 24713}, {\"ngram\": \"the government\", \"from\": 24717, \"to\": 24731}, {\"ngram\": \"the centre\", \"from\": 24735, \"to\": 24745}, {\"ngram\": \"many more girls\", \"from\": 24747, \"to\": 24762}, {\"ngram\": \"Vinesh Phogat\", \"from\": 24806, \"to\": 24819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On June 7, after assurances from the then sports minister, Anurag Thakur, that a charge sheet against Singh would be filed soon, and that neither Singh's family members nor his associates would be allowed to contest the WFI elections, the wrestlers called off their protest.\", \"from\": 24827, \"to\": 25101, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 24886, \"end\": 24899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anurag_Thakur\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anurag Thakur\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anurag_Thakur\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anurag_Thakur\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 24830, \"to\": 24834}, {\"ngram\": \"assurances\", \"from\": 24844, \"to\": 24854}, {\"ngram\": \"the then sports minister\", \"from\": 24860, \"to\": 24884}, {\"ngram\": \"a charge sheet\", \"from\": 24906, \"to\": 24920}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 24929, \"to\": 24934}, {\"ngram\": \"neither Singh's family members\", \"from\": 24965, \"to\": 24995}, {\"ngram\": \"his associates\", \"from\": 25000, \"to\": 25014}, {\"ngram\": \"the WFI elections\", \"from\": 25043, \"to\": 25060}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrestlers\", \"from\": 25062, \"to\": 25075}, {\"ngram\": \"their protest\", \"from\": 25087, \"to\": 25100}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the next day, the father of the child wrestler said the complaint his daughter had filed against Singh was false.\", \"from\": 25103, \"to\": 25220, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the father\", \"from\": 25121, \"to\": 25131}, {\"ngram\": \"the child wrestler\", \"from\": 25135, \"to\": 25153}, {\"ngram\": \"the complaint\", \"from\": 25159, \"to\": 25172}, {\"ngram\": \"his daughter\", \"from\": 25173, \"to\": 25185}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 25204, \"to\": 25209}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two months later, an obscene 30-second clip with Anshu Malik's morphed photo went viral.\", \"from\": 25221, \"to\": 25309, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25270, \"end\": 25281, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anshu_Malik\", \"score\": 0.9999999894843086, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Anshu Malik\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anshu_Malik\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Anshu_Malik\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an obscene 30-second clip\", \"from\": 25239, \"to\": 25264}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Police arrested a man and claimed that he had created the clip to increase his followers, but Vinesh and Sakshi accused Singh's team of being behind the video.\", \"from\": 25310, \"to\": 25469, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25404, \"end\": 25410, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}, {\"begin\": 25415, \"end\": 25421, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Shivanand\", \"score\": 0.9999999999937472, \"rank\": 5.960319785234944e-12, \"text\": \"Sakshi\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Shivanand\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sakshi_Shivanand\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Police\", \"from\": 25310, \"to\": 25316}, {\"ngram\": \"a man\", \"from\": 25326, \"to\": 25331}, {\"ngram\": \"the clip\", \"from\": 25364, \"to\": 25372}, {\"ngram\": \"his followers\", \"from\": 25385, \"to\": 25398}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh's team\", \"from\": 25430, \"to\": 25442}, {\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 25459, \"to\": 25468}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet again, after smelling victory, India's champion wrestlers were being tested afresh.\", \"from\": 25471, \"to\": 25558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25506, \"end\": 25511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9401769988790823, \"rank\": 0.06362926176552183, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 25497, \"to\": 25504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But their sport and background had trained them well.\", \"from\": 25559, \"to\": 25612, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their sport\", \"from\": 25563, \"to\": 25574}, {\"ngram\": \"background\", \"from\": 25579, \"to\": 25589}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Eighty percent of the wrestlers are from poor families.\", \"from\": 25614, \"to\": 25670, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Eighty percent\", \"from\": 25615, \"to\": 25629}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrestlers\", \"from\": 25633, \"to\": 25646}, {\"ngram\": \"poor families\", \"from\": 25656, \"to\": 25669}]}, {\"sentence\": \"No kid from a rich family will subject themselves to this kind of torture,\\\" said Sanjay Sihag of Altius Wrestling Academy as he watched one of his students, Pinky, winded and with tears rolling down her cheeks, crawl off the mat's red zone - a circle, nine metres in diameter, that demarcates the wrestling arena - on her elbows.\", \"from\": 25671, \"to\": 26000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 25752, \"end\": 25758, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanjay_Gandhi\", \"score\": 0.9844422896173002, \"rank\": 0.010621397576648137, \"text\": \"Sanjay\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanjay_Gandhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanjay_Gandhi\"}, {\"begin\": 25828, \"end\": 25833, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinky_and_the_Brain\", \"score\": 0.9999947473243475, \"rank\": 4.695426819857514e-06, \"text\": \"Pinky\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q15416\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinky_and_the_Brain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinky_and_the_Brain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"No kid\", \"from\": 25671, \"to\": 25677}, {\"ngram\": \"a rich family\", \"from\": 25683, \"to\": 25696}, {\"ngram\": \"this kind\", \"from\": 25724, \"to\": 25733}, {\"ngram\": \"torture\", \"from\": 25737, \"to\": 25744}, {\"ngram\": \"Altius Wrestling Academy\", \"from\": 25768, \"to\": 25792}, {\"ngram\": \"his students\", \"from\": 25814, \"to\": 25826}, {\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 25851, \"to\": 25856}, {\"ngram\": \"her cheeks\", \"from\": 25870, \"to\": 25880}, {\"ngram\": \"the mat's red zone\", \"from\": 25892, \"to\": 25910}, {\"ngram\": \"a circle\", \"from\": 25913, \"to\": 25921}, {\"ngram\": \"nine metres\", \"from\": 25923, \"to\": 25934}, {\"ngram\": \"diameter\", \"from\": 25938, \"to\": 25946}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrestling arena\", \"from\": 25964, \"to\": 25983}, {\"ngram\": \"her elbows\", \"from\": 25989, \"to\": 25999}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In wrestling bouts - two rounds of three minutes each, with a 30-second break in between - points are won by throwing the opponent, locking them in a grip, or takedowns.\", \"from\": 26002, \"to\": 26171, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"bouts\", \"from\": 26015, \"to\": 26020}, {\"ngram\": \"two rounds\", \"from\": 26023, \"to\": 26033}, {\"ngram\": \"three minutes\", \"from\": 26037, \"to\": 26050}, {\"ngram\": \"a 30-second break\", \"from\": 26062, \"to\": 26079}, {\"ngram\": \"between - points\", \"from\": 26083, \"to\": 26099}, {\"ngram\": \"the opponent\", \"from\": 26120, \"to\": 26132}, {\"ngram\": \"a grip\", \"from\": 26150, \"to\": 26156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Knee, elbow and shoulder injuries are common.\", \"from\": 26172, \"to\": 26217, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Knee\", \"from\": 26172, \"to\": 26176}, {\"ngram\": \"elbow\", \"from\": 26178, \"to\": 26183}, {\"ngram\": \"shoulder injuries\", \"from\": 26188, \"to\": 26205}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To be fighting fit, wrestlers at Altius follow a back-breaking daily routine of physical training and mat practice, supplemented by a protein-rich, nutritious diet.\", \"from\": 26219, \"to\": 26383, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"wrestlers\", \"from\": 26239, \"to\": 26248}, {\"ngram\": \"Altius\", \"from\": 26252, \"to\": 26258}, {\"ngram\": \"a back-breaking daily routine\", \"from\": 26266, \"to\": 26295}, {\"ngram\": \"physical training\", \"from\": 26299, \"to\": 26316}, {\"ngram\": \"mat practice\", \"from\": 26321, \"to\": 26333}, {\"ngram\": \"a protein-rich, nutritious diet\", \"from\": 26351, \"to\": 26382}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All hostel rooms have large sacks of California almonds, crates of sweet lemon, mortars and pestles, strange juicer contraptions and massage oil bottles.\", \"from\": 26384, \"to\": 26537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 26421, \"end\": 26431, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"score\": 0.9993742777410856, \"rank\": 0.0006054867577658535, \"text\": \"California\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/California\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All hostel rooms\", \"from\": 26384, \"to\": 26400}, {\"ngram\": \"large sacks\", \"from\": 26406, \"to\": 26417}, {\"ngram\": \"crates\", \"from\": 26441, \"to\": 26447}, {\"ngram\": \"sweet lemon\", \"from\": 26451, \"to\": 26462}, {\"ngram\": \"mortars\", \"from\": 26464, \"to\": 26471}, {\"ngram\": \"pestles\", \"from\": 26476, \"to\": 26483}, {\"ngram\": \"strange juicer contraptions\", \"from\": 26485, \"to\": 26512}, {\"ngram\": \"massage oil bottles\", \"from\": 26517, \"to\": 26536}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Though there is an abundance of fresh milk, curd and butter, hostel meals are simple and strictly vegetarian except for eggs in the morning.\", \"from\": 26539, \"to\": 26679, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an abundance\", \"from\": 26555, \"to\": 26567}, {\"ngram\": \"fresh milk\", \"from\": 26571, \"to\": 26581}, {\"ngram\": \"curd\", \"from\": 26583, \"to\": 26587}, {\"ngram\": \"butter\", \"from\": 26592, \"to\": 26598}, {\"ngram\": \"hostel meals\", \"from\": 26600, \"to\": 26612}, {\"ngram\": \"eggs\", \"from\": 26659, \"to\": 26663}, {\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 26667, \"to\": 26678}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All lentils and vegetables are free of red chilli powder and traditional Indian spices for easy digestion, and taste a little bland, like baby-food.\", \"from\": 26680, \"to\": 26828, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 26753, \"end\": 26766, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spice_trade\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Indian spices\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spice_trade\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spice_trade\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All lentils\", \"from\": 26680, \"to\": 26691}, {\"ngram\": \"vegetables\", \"from\": 26696, \"to\": 26706}, {\"ngram\": \"red chilli powder\", \"from\": 26719, \"to\": 26736}, {\"ngram\": \"easy digestion\", \"from\": 26771, \"to\": 26785}, {\"ngram\": \"baby-food\", \"from\": 26818, \"to\": 26827}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Yet, in a state with a per capita monthly income of about 25,000 Indian rupees ($298), the monthly average expense that parents need to shell out on a wrestler at Altius is in excess of 20,000 rupees ($215).\", \"from\": 26830, \"to\": 27037, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 26895, \"end\": 26908, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_rupee\", \"score\": 0.9606837377126767, \"rank\": 0.04092529179367022, \"text\": \"Indian rupees\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_rupee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_rupee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a state\", \"from\": 26838, \"to\": 26845}, {\"ngram\": \"a per capita monthly income\", \"from\": 26851, \"to\": 26878}, {\"ngram\": \"the monthly average expense\", \"from\": 26917, \"to\": 26944}, {\"ngram\": \"parents\", \"from\": 26950, \"to\": 26957}, {\"ngram\": \"a wrestler\", \"from\": 26979, \"to\": 26989}, {\"ngram\": \"Altius\", \"from\": 26993, \"to\": 26999}, {\"ngram\": \"excess\", \"from\": 27006, \"to\": 27012}, {\"ngram\": \"20,000 rupees\", \"from\": 27016, \"to\": 27029}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That includes the academy's fee of 8,000 rupees, and the cost of wrestlers' special diet and kit (at least 10,000 rupees).\", \"from\": 27038, \"to\": 27160, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the academy's fee\", \"from\": 27052, \"to\": 27069}, {\"ngram\": \"8,000 rupees\", \"from\": 27073, \"to\": 27085}, {\"ngram\": \"the cost\", \"from\": 27091, \"to\": 27099}, {\"ngram\": \"wrestlers' special diet\", \"from\": 27103, \"to\": 27126}, {\"ngram\": \"kit\", \"from\": 27131, \"to\": 27134}, {\"ngram\": \"(at least 10,000 rupees\", \"from\": 27135, \"to\": 27158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Many fathers and mothers in Haryana struggle and cut other expenses to put their kids through wrestling academies.\", \"from\": 27162, \"to\": 27276, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 27190, \"end\": 27197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 0.999985691800293, \"rank\": 1.4306447970300157e-05, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Many fathers\", \"from\": 27162, \"to\": 27174}, {\"ngram\": \"mothers\", \"from\": 27179, \"to\": 27186}, {\"ngram\": \"other expenses\", \"from\": 27215, \"to\": 27229}, {\"ngram\": \"their kids\", \"from\": 27237, \"to\": 27247}, {\"ngram\": \"wrestling academies\", \"from\": 27256, \"to\": 27275}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Some sell patches of their farmland, move to cities like Rohtak and live in rented homes just so their daughters can have a shot at wrestling glory.\", \"from\": 27277, \"to\": 27425, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 27334, \"end\": 27340, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohtak_district\", \"score\": 0.9984480999883956, \"rank\": 0.0015543121486816574, \"text\": \"Rohtak\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohtak_district\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohtak_district\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Some sell patches\", \"from\": 27277, \"to\": 27294}, {\"ngram\": \"their farmland\", \"from\": 27298, \"to\": 27312}, {\"ngram\": \"cities\", \"from\": 27322, \"to\": 27328}, {\"ngram\": \"rented homes\", \"from\": 27353, \"to\": 27365}, {\"ngram\": \"their daughters\", \"from\": 27374, \"to\": 27389}, {\"ngram\": \"a shot\", \"from\": 27399, \"to\": 27405}, {\"ngram\": \"wrestling glory\", \"from\": 27409, \"to\": 27424}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's why, Sanjay said, the first priority for all wrestlers is to get a job.\", \"from\": 27427, \"to\": 27505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 27439, \"end\": 27445, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanjay_Khan\", \"score\": 0.7513970872547305, \"rank\": 0.31011446639821394, \"text\": \"Sanjay\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanjay_Khan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanjay_Khan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first priority\", \"from\": 27452, \"to\": 27470}, {\"ngram\": \"all wrestlers\", \"from\": 27475, \"to\": 27488}, {\"ngram\": \"a job\", \"from\": 27499, \"to\": 27504}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Once that is secure, then they play for fame, glory.\\\"\", \"from\": 27506, \"to\": 27560, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fame\", \"from\": 27547, \"to\": 27551}, {\"ngram\": \"glory\", \"from\": 27553, \"to\": 27558}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The federal and state governments, Indian Railways, the armed forces and police services offer jobs to exceptional sportspersons.\", \"from\": 27562, \"to\": 27691, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 27597, \"end\": 27612, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Railways\", \"score\": 0.9997866262735075, \"rank\": 0.00021341926451111577, \"text\": \"Indian Railways\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Railways\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Indian_Railways\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the armed forces\", \"from\": 27614, \"to\": 27630}, {\"ngram\": \"police services\", \"from\": 27635, \"to\": 27650}, {\"ngram\": \"jobs\", \"from\": 27657, \"to\": 27661}, {\"ngram\": \"exceptional sportspersons\", \"from\": 27665, \"to\": 27690}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The bigger the game and the medal, the better the job and the pay.\", \"from\": 27692, \"to\": 27758, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The bigger the game\", \"from\": 27692, \"to\": 27711}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal\", \"from\": 27716, \"to\": 27725}, {\"ngram\": \"the better the job\", \"from\": 27727, \"to\": 27745}, {\"ngram\": \"the pay\", \"from\": 27750, \"to\": 27757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Companies, too, offer sponsorships to young wrestlers.\", \"from\": 27759, \"to\": 27813, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Companies\", \"from\": 27759, \"to\": 27768}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsorships\", \"from\": 27781, \"to\": 27793}, {\"ngram\": \"young wrestlers\", \"from\": 27797, \"to\": 27812}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Swati, 18, a rising star at Altius who is chasing a gold medal in nationals, recently bagged one.\", \"from\": 27815, \"to\": 27912, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 27815, \"end\": 27820, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shudra\", \"score\": 0.7300245190596952, \"rank\": 0.34023643021768657, \"text\": \"Swati\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shudra\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Shudra\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a rising star\", \"from\": 27826, \"to\": 27839}, {\"ngram\": \"Altius\", \"from\": 27843, \"to\": 27849}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 27865, \"to\": 27877}, {\"ngram\": \"nationals\", \"from\": 27881, \"to\": 27890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Every month, 12,000 rupees now land directly in her bank account, a big relief for her parents, both of whom are teachers and have physical disabilities.\", \"from\": 27913, \"to\": 28066, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"12,000 rupees\", \"from\": 27926, \"to\": 27939}, {\"ngram\": \"her bank account\", \"from\": 27961, \"to\": 27977}, {\"ngram\": \"a big relief\", \"from\": 27979, \"to\": 27991}, {\"ngram\": \"her parents\", \"from\": 27996, \"to\": 28007}, {\"ngram\": \"teachers\", \"from\": 28026, \"to\": 28034}, {\"ngram\": \"physical disabilities\", \"from\": 28044, \"to\": 28065}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This economic independence is precious for Haryana's women wrestlers.\", \"from\": 28