 \"to\": 28356}, {\"ngram\": \"even their own village\", \"from\": 28361, \"to\": 28383}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lying on her bed at Altius, a pink towel wrapped around her neck, Tanu Sharma, 18, laughed as she recalled a girl at her women-only college who asked her recently: \\\"Brother, are you a boy or a girl?\\\"\", \"from\": 28398, \"to\": 28597, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her bed\", \"from\": 28407, \"to\": 28414}, {\"ngram\": \"Altius\", \"from\": 28418, \"to\": 28424}, {\"ngram\": \"a pink towel\", \"from\": 28426, \"to\": 28438}, {\"ngram\": \"her neck\", \"from\": 28454, \"to\": 28462}, {\"ngram\": \"Tanu Sharma\", \"from\": 28464, \"to\": 28475}, {\"ngram\": \"a girl\", \"from\": 28505, \"to\": 28511}, {\"ngram\": \"her women-only college\", \"from\": 28515, \"to\": 28537}, {\"ngram\": \"a boy\", \"from\": 28580, \"to\": 28585}, {\"ngram\": \"a girl\", \"from\": 28589, \"to\": 28595}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tall and lanky, Tanu does not care.\", \"from\": 28599, \"to\": 28634, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tanu\", \"from\": 28615, \"to\": 28619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She wears only shorts or trousers and dreams of the day when she will drive her own car, wearing dark glasses, speakers blasting out music.\", \"from\": 28635, \"to\": 28774, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"only shorts\", \"from\": 28645, \"to\": 28656}, {\"ngram\": \"trousers\", \"from\": 28660, \"to\": 28668}, {\"ngram\": \"dreams\", \"from\": 28673, \"to\": 28679}, {\"ngram\": \"the day\", \"from\": 28683, \"to\": 28690}, {\"ngram\": \"her own car\", \"from\": 28711, \"to\": 28722}, {\"ngram\": \"dark glasses\", \"from\": 28732, \"to\": 28744}, {\"ngram\": \"speakers\", \"from\": 28746, \"to\": 28754}, {\"ngram\": \"music\", \"from\": 28768, \"to\": 28773}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like most wrestlers, she, too, is working towards winning an international medal that will guarantee her the job of a deputy superintendent of police - a position of power, swag and official cars with beacon lights.\", \"from\": 28776, \"to\": 28991, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"most wrestlers\", \"from\": 28781, \"to\": 28795}, {\"ngram\": \"an international medal\", \"from\": 28834, \"to\": 28856}, {\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 28881, \"to\": 28888}, {\"ngram\": \"a deputy superintendent\", \"from\": 28892, \"to\": 28915}, {\"ngram\": \"police\", \"from\": 28919, \"to\": 28925}, {\"ngram\": \"a position\", \"from\": 28928, \"to\": 28938}, {\"ngram\": \"power\", \"from\": 28942, \"to\": 28947}, {\"ngram\": \"swag\", \"from\": 28949, \"to\": 28953}, {\"ngram\": \"official cars\", \"from\": 28958, \"to\": 28971}, {\"ngram\": \"beacon lights\", \"from\": 28977, \"to\": 28990}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"This life is so much better,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 28993, \"to\": 29033, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This life\", \"from\": 28994, \"to\": 29003}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I can marry, have a family.\", \"from\": 29034, \"to\": 29062, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a family\", \"from\": 29053, \"to\": 29061}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But they [girls who are not seeking a sports career] can never play like me, or live the life I am living.\", \"from\": 29063, \"to\": 29169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 29073, \"to\": 29078}, {\"ngram\": \"a sports career\", \"from\": 29099, \"to\": 29114}, {\"ngram\": \"the life\", \"from\": 29148, \"to\": 29156}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Your whole life changes with wrestling.\", \"from\": 29170, \"to\": 29209, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Your whole life\", \"from\": 29170, \"to\": 29185}, {\"ngram\": \"wrestling\", \"from\": 29199, \"to\": 29208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"You earn money, you are not dependent on anyone.\\\"\", \"from\": 29210, \"to\": 29259, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"money\", \"from\": 29219, \"to\": 29224}, {\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 29251, \"to\": 29257}]}, {\"sentence\": \"To free the WFI from Singh's clutches, the wrestlers fielded their own ticket - led by a veteran female grappler - for the elections to the wrestling federation, when they were finally held last December.\", \"from\": 29261, \"to\": 29465, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the WFI\", \"from\": 29269, \"to\": 29276}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh's clutches\", \"from\": 29282, \"to\": 29298}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrestlers\", \"from\": 29300, \"to\": 29313}, {\"ngram\": \"their own ticket\", \"from\": 29322, \"to\": 29338}, {\"ngram\": \"a veteran female grappler\", \"from\": 29348, \"to\": 29373}, {\"ngram\": \"the elections\", \"from\": 29380, \"to\": 29393}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrestling federation\", \"from\": 29397, \"to\": 29421}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But Singh's panel won 13 of the 15 posts.\", \"from\": 29467, \"to\": 29508, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Singh's panel\", \"from\": 29471, \"to\": 29484}, {\"ngram\": \"the 15 posts\", \"from\": 29495, \"to\": 29507}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sanjay Singh, an old associate from Uttar Pradesh who called Singh his \\\"elder brother\\\" and had held several positions at WFI over the years, all of them subordinate to Singh, was elected WFI's new president.\", \"from\": 29509, \"to\": 29716, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 29509, \"end\": 29521, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanjaya_Sinh\", \"score\": 0.9999999999998863, \"rank\": 8.541558523689688e-14, \"text\": \"Sanjay Singh\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanjaya_Sinh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sanjaya_Sinh\"}, {\"begin\": 29545, \"end\": 29558, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uttar_Pradesh\", \"score\": 0.9999994598748894, \"rank\": 5.401055987941093e-07, \"text\": \"Uttar Pradesh\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uttar_Pradesh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uttar_Pradesh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an old associate\", \"from\": 29523, \"to\": 29539}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 29570, \"to\": 29575}, {\"ngram\": \"his \\\"elder brother\", \"from\": 29576, \"to\": 29594}, {\"ngram\": \"several positions\", \"from\": 29609, \"to\": 29626}, {\"ngram\": \"WFI\", \"from\": 29630, \"to\": 29633}, {\"ngram\": \"the years\", \"from\": 29639, \"to\": 29648}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 29677, \"to\": 29682}, {\"ngram\": \"WFI's new president\", \"from\": 29696, \"to\": 29715}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The same day he announced that national competitions for the Under 15 and Under 20 categories would be held in Singh's hometown, Gonda.\", \"from\": 29717, \"to\": 29852, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 29846, \"end\": 29851, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gonda_district\", \"score\": 0.9999999761847679, \"rank\": 2.2980105623108695e-08, \"text\": \"Gonda\", \"types\": [\"Q3455524\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gonda_district\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gonda_district\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"national competitions\", \"from\": 29748, \"to\": 29769}, {\"ngram\": \"the Under 15 and Under 20 categories\", \"from\": 29774, \"to\": 29810}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh's hometown\", \"from\": 29828, \"to\": 29844}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A year after winning a Commonwealth Games gold, and seven years after her bronze medal at the Rio Olympics that changed the face of Indian women's wrestling, 31-year-old Sakhi Malik could take it no more.\", \"from\": 29854, \"to\": 30058, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 29877, \"end\": 29895, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"score\": 0.9846786267225418, \"rank\": 0.012695633583076165, \"text\": \"Commonwealth Games\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Commonwealth_Games\"}, {\"begin\": 29986, \"end\": 29998, \"title\": \"ht