 after the notice, Nada issued what the guardian calls, \\\"a clean chit\\\" to the wrestler who had complained against Singh.\", \"from\": 33289, \"to\": 33439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 33338, \"end\": 33342, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RK_Nada_Split\", \"score\": 0.9999995957227519, \"rank\": 1.52103240156599e-07, \"text\": \"Nada\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RK_Nada_Split\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/RK_Nada_Split\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 33292, \"to\": 33295}, {\"ngram\": \"the notice\", \"from\": 33326, \"to\": 33336}, {\"ngram\": \"the guardian\", \"from\": 33355, \"to\": 33367}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"a clean chit\", \"from\": 33375, \"to\": 33388}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrestler\", \"from\": 33393, \"to\": 33405}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 33433, \"to\": 33438}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it was too late: With the sponsorship deal gone, she had lost the funding support she needed to improve her fitness levels, train abroad, participate in international tournaments and improve her ranking before this year's Olympic trials.\", \"from\": 33440, \"to\": 33681, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the sponsorship deal\", \"from\": 33466, \"to\": 33486}, {\"ngram\": \"the funding support\", \"from\": 33506, \"to\": 33525}, {\"ngram\": \"her fitness levels\", \"from\": 33548, \"to\": 33566}, {\"ngram\": \"international tournaments\", \"from\": 33597, \"to\": 33622}, {\"ngram\": \"her ranking\", \"from\": 33635, \"to\": 33646}, {\"ngram\": \"this year's Olympic trials\", \"from\": 33654, \"to\": 33680}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Al Jazeera sent detailed questions to Reliance Foundation Youth Sports on the wrestler's case on May 21, but has not received any response.\", \"from\": 33683, \"to\": 33822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 33683, \"end\": 33693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 0.9961378233201462, \"rank\": 0.0021