upied.\", \"from\": 35175, \"to\": 35231, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"several beds\", \"from\": 35179, \"to\": 35191}, {\"ngram\": \"his hostel rooms\", \"from\": 35195, \"to\": 35211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Lots of parents have made their daughters quit wrestling after protests and inaction over Brij Bhushan.\", \"from\": 35232, \"to\": 35336, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lots\", \"from\": 35233, \"to\": 35237}, {\"ngram\": \"parents\", \"from\": 35241, \"to\": 35248}, {\"ngram\": \"their daughters\", \"from\": 35259, \"to\": 35274}, {\"ngram\": \"wrestling\", \"from\": 35280, \"to\": 35289}, {\"ngram\": \"protests\", \"from\": 35296, \"to\": 35304}, {\"ngram\": \"inaction\", \"from\": 35309, \"to\": 35317}, {\"ngram\": \"Brij Bhushan\", \"from\": 35323, \"to\": 35335}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And those who have quit are not even studying.\", \"from\": 35337, \"to\": 35383, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"They are mostly just doing household work,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 35384, \"to\": 35436, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"household work\", \"from\": 35411, \"to\": 35425}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Esha lives with her family next door to Virender's academy.\", \"from\": 35438, \"to\": 35497, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Esha\", \"from\": 35438, \"to\": 35442}, {\"ngram\": \"her family\", \"from\": 35454, \"to\": 35464}, {\"ngram\": \"Virender's academy\", \"from\": 35478, \"to\": 35496}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her family owns a small patch of farmland where they grow pearl millet and wheat.\", \"from\": 35498, \"to\": 35579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her family\", \"from\": 35498, \"to\": 35508}, {\"ngram\": \"a small patch\", \"from\": 35514, \"to\": 35527}, {\"ngram\": \"farmland\", \"from\": 35531, \"to\": 35539}, {\"ngram\": \"pearl millet\", \"from\": 35556, \"to\": 35568}, {\"ngram\": \"wheat\", \"from\": 35573, \"to\": 35578}]}, {\"sen