7}, {\"ngram\": \"her mother\", \"from\": 35850, \"to\": 35860}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But when I saw this Brij Bhushan protest on TV, I got scared.\", \"from\": 35887, \"to\": 35949, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this Brij Bhushan\", \"from\": 35903, \"to\": 35920}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 35932, \"to\": 35934}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If she goes for competitions, this can happen to her as well.\\\"\", \"from\": 35950, \"to\": 36012, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 35966, \"to\": 35978}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Esha's father can not accompany her to competitions, and Mamata is often laid up in bed because of her slipped disk.\", \"from\": 36014, \"to\": 36130, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 36071, \"end\": 36077, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mamata_Banerjee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mamata\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mamata_Banerjee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mamata_Banerjee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Esha's father\", \"from\": 36014, \"to\": 36027}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 36053, \"to\": 36065}, {\"ngram\": \"bed\", \"from\": 36098, \"to\": 36101}, {\"ngram\": \"her slipped disk\", \"from\": 36113, \"to\": 36129}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If this Brij Bhushan issue had not happened, we would have made her continue, at least till she got a job,\\\" said Mamata.\", \"from\": 36131, \"to\": 36252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 36245, \"end\": 36251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mamata_Banerjee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Mamata\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mamata_Banerjee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mamata_Banerjee\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this Brij Bhushan issue\", \"from\": 36135, \"to\": 36158}, {\"ngram\": \"a job\", \"from\": 36232, \"to\": 36237}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Esha quit wrestling last year and is now waiting to get married in a twin wedding ceremony along with her elder sister because that is cost effective.\", \"from\": 36254, \"to\": 36404, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Esha\", \"from\": 36254, \"to\": 36258}, {\"ngram\": \"wrestling\", \"from\": 36264, \"to\": 36273}, {\"ngram\": \"a twin wedding ceremony\", \"from\": 36321, \"to\": 36344}, {\"ngram\": \"her elder sister\", \"from\": 36356, \"to\": 36372}, {\"ngram\": \"cost\", \"from\": 36389, \"to\": 36393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Like Esha, Sheetal Dalal had been training at Virender's academy - for more than five years.\", \"from\": 36406, \"to\": 36498, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Esha\", \"from\": 36411, \"to\": 36415}, {\"ngram\": \"Sheetal Dalal\", \"from\": 36417, \"to\": 36430}, {\"ngram\": \"Virender's academy\", \"from\": 36452, \"to\": 36470}, {\"ngram\": \"more than five years\", \"from\": 36477, \"to\": 36497}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A year before the protest, the 19-year-old won a silver medal in a national tournament.\", \"from\": 36499, \"to\": 36586, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the protest\", \"from\": 36513, \"to\": 36524}, {\"ngram\": \"a silver medal\", \"from\": 36546, \"to\": 36560}, {\"ngram\": \"a national tournament\", \"from\": 36564, \"to\": 36585}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But last year, on her parents' insistence, she quit wrestling and now sells soap, shampoo, mosquito repellent coils and hair oil at a shop nearby.\", \"from\": 36587, \"to\": 36733, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 36678, \"end\": 36686, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mosquito\", \"score\": 0.9999754758740861, \"rank\": 2.326876050165204e-05, \"text\": \"mosquito\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mosquito\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mosquito\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her parents' insistence\", \"from\