to\": 37746}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual harassment\", \"from\": 37799, \"to\": 37816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Haryana Wrestling Association, which was until last year relatively free of Singh's influence, is now headed by Ramesh Bohar, Singh's close aide, who has faced several criminal cases.\", \"from\": 37818, \"to\": 38005, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 37822, \"end\": 37829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 0.9999999999948841, \"rank\": 4.597455687058864e-12, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}, {\"begin\": 37934, \"end\": 37940, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ramesh_Sippy\", \"score\": 0.5854239635445158, \"rank\": 0.5590512461971445, \"text\": \"Ramesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ramesh_Sippy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ramesh_Sippy\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"last year\", \"from\": 37869, \"to\": 37878}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh's influence\", \"from\": 37898, \"to\": 37915}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh's close aide\", \"from\": 37948, \"to\": 37966}, {\"ngram\": \"several criminal cases\", \"from\": 37982, \"to\": 38004}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In India's recently held national elections, the BJP dropped Singh as a candidate, but fielded his son from the same constituency.\", \"from\": 38007, \"to\": 38137, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 38010, \"end\": 38015, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.9997963408886442, \"rank\": 0.0002003591609637009, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}, {\"begin\": 38056, \"end\": 38059, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 0.9999656300073543, \"rank\": 3.353942275706545e-05, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 38068, \"to\": 38073}, {\"ngram\": \"a candidate\", \"from\": 38077, \"to\": 38088}, {\"ngram\": \"his son\", \"from\": 38102, \"to\": 38109}, {\"ngram\": \"the same constituency\", \"from\": 38115, \"to\": 38136}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have neither aged nor have I retired.\", \"from\": 38138, \"to\": 38178, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am now like a 'chutta sand' (stray bull) who can take on anybody,\\\" Singh said while campaigning.\", \"from\": 38179, \"to\": 38277, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a 'chutta sand\", \"from\": 38193, \"to\": 38207}, {\"ngram\": \"(stray bull\", \"from\": 38209, \"to\": 38220}, {\"ngram\": \"anybody\", \"from\": 38238, \"to\": 38245}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 38248, \"to\": 38253}]}, {\"sentence\": \"His son, Karan Bhushan Singh, is now a member of parliament and the president of the Uttar Pradesh Wrestling Association.\", \"from\": 38279, \"to\": 38400, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 38288, \"end\": 38293, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karna\", \"score\": 0.9936231125379283, \"rank\": 0.006408167690755002, \"text\": \"Karan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karna\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Karna\"}, {\"begin\": 38364, \"end\": 38377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uttar_Pradesh\", \"score\": 0.9999011405267084, \"rank\": 8.056775406920476e-05, \"text\": \"Uttar Pradesh\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uttar_Pradesh\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Uttar_Pradesh\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"His son\", \"from\": 38279, \"to\": 38286}, {\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 38316, \"to\": 38324}, {\"ngram\": \"parliament\", \"from\": 38328, \"to\": 38338}, {\"ngram\": \"the president\", \"from\": 38343, \"to\": 38356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In May this year, a court in New Delhi, while framing charges against Singh in the sexual harassment case, noted that there was a clear \\\"unity of purpose\\\" behind Singh's actions to \\\"sexually exploit vulnerable female subordinates as much as possible\\\".\", \"from\": 38402, \"to\": 38653, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 38431, \"end\": 38440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"score\": 0.8591676958685235, \"rank\": 0.16229432338755895, \"text\": \"New Delhi\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_Delhi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"May\", \"from\": 38405, \"to\": 38408}, {\"ngram\": \"a court\", \"from\": 38420, \"to\": 38427}, {\"ngram\": \"charges\", \"from\": 38456, \"to\": 38463}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 38472, \"to\": 38477}, {\"ngram\": \"the sexual harassment case\", \"from\": 38481, \"to\": 38507}, {\"ngram\": \"a clear \\\"unity\", \"from\": 38530, \"to\": 38544}, {\"ngram\": \"purpose\", \"from\": 38548, \"to\": 38555}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh's actions\", \"from\": 38564, \"to\": 38579}, {\"ngram\": \"vulnerable female subordinates\", \"from\": 38601, \"to\": 38631}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The court noted that it had found sufficient material in the police's charge sheet against Singh to frame charges and begin the trial.\", \"from\": 38654, \"to\": 38788, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The court\", \"from\": 38654, \"to\": 38663}, {\"ngram\": \"sufficient material\", \"from\": 38688, \"to\": 38707}, {\"ngram\": \"the police's charge sheet\", \"from\": 38711, \"to\": 38736}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh\", \"from\": 38745, \"to\": 38750}, {\"ngram\": \"charges\", \"from\": 38760, \"to\": 38767}, {\"ngram\": \"the trial\", \"from\": 38778, \"to\": 38787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a moment of victory for the protesting wrestlers.\", \"from\": 38790, \"to\": 38846, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a moment\", \"from\": 38797, \"to\": 38805}, {\"ngram\": \"victory\", \"from\": 38809, \"to\": 38816}, {\"ngram\": \"the protesting wrestlers\", \"from\": 38821, \"to\": 38845}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Our name had been tainted and no one believed us.\", \"from\": 38847, \"to\": 38897, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Our name\", \"from\": 38848, \"to\": 38856}, {\"ngram\": \"no one\", \"from\": 38878, \"to\": 38884}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 38894, \"to\": 38896}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But the court vindicated us when it said that there is proof of sexual harassment,\\\" a wrestler involved in the case said.\", \"from\": 38898, \"to\": 39019, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the court\", \"from\": 38902, \"to\": 38911}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 38923, \"to\": 38925}, {\"ngram\": \"proof\", \"from\": 38953, \"to\": 38958}, {\"ngram\": \"sexual harassment\", \"from\": 38962, \"to\": 38979}, {\"ngram\": \"a wrestler\", \"from\": 38982, \"to\": 38992}, {\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 39005, \"to\": 39013}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But two days later, he said, one of their supporters \\\"who is not even a wrestler\\\" got a threatening call from an unknown number.\", \"from\": 39021, \"to\": 39149, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their supporters\", \"from\": 39057, \"to\": 39073}, {\"ngram\": \"even a wrestler\", \"from\": 39086, \"to\": 39101}, {\"ngram\": \"a threatening call\", \"from\": 39107, \"to\": 39125}, {\"ngram\": \"an unknown number\", \"from\": 39131, \"to\": 39148}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A wrestling coach in Rohtak, who trains one of the complainants, told Al Jazeera that Singh's men have been calling the parents of his students and telling them to withdraw their kids from his academy or risk getting them entangled in a dope case.\", \"from\": 39151, \"to\": 39398, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 39172, \"end\": 39178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohtak\", \"score\": 0.9998570397490573, \"rank\": 0.00014297840935627746, \"text\": \"Rohtak\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\", \"Q3957\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohtak\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rohtak\"}, {\"begin\": 39221, \"end\": 39231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 0.9999712493768683, \"rank\": 2.8414278160104182e-05, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A wrestling coach\", \"from\": 39151, \"to\": 39168}, {\"ngram\": \"the complainants\", \"from\": 39198, \"to\": 39214}, {\"ngram\": \"Singh's men\", \"from\": 39237, \"to\": 39248}, {\"ngram\": \"the parents\", \"from\": 39267, \"to\": 39278}, {\"ngram\": \"his students\", \"from\": 39282, \"to\": 39294}, {\"ngram\": \"their kids\", \"from\": 39324, \"to\": 39334}, {\"ngram\": \"his academy\", \"from\": 39340, \"to\": 39351}, {\"ngram\": \"risk\", \"from\": 39355, \"to\": 39359}, {\"ngram\": \"a dope case\", \"from\": 39386, \"to\": 39397}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I had 50 girls and about 10 boys in my wrestling academy.\", \"from\": 39400, \"to\": 39458, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"50 girls\", \"from\": 39407, \"to\": 39415}, {\"ngram\": \"about 10 boys\", \"from\": 39420, \"to\": 39433}, {\"ngram\": \"my wrestling academy\", \"from\": 39437, \"to\": 39457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now my strength is down to 37-38,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 39459, \"to\": 39502, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my strength\", \"from\": 39463, \"to\": 39474}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He worries that with the court case on, harassment will increase.\", \"from\": 39504, \"to\": 39569, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the court case\", \"from\": 39525, \"to\": 39539}, {\"ngram\": \"harassment\", \"from\": 39544, \"to\": 39554}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Witnesses will disappear or turn hostile,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 39570, \"to\": 39622, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Witnesses\", \"from\": 39571, \"to\": 39580}]}, {\"sentence\": \"One complainant agreed to talk to Al Jazeera about the case and the intimidation she was facing.\", \"from\": 39624, \"to\": 39720, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 39658, \"end\": 39668, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 0.9999712493768683, \"rank\": 2.8414278160104182e-05, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"One complainant\", \"from\": 39624, \"to\": 39639}, {\"ngram\": \"the case\", \"from\": 39675, \"to\": 39683}, {\"ngram\": \"the intimidation\", \"from\": 39688, \"to\": 39704}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But after exchanging messages for several days and saying that she was trying to muster courage, she finally texted, \\\"Sorry, it's become really very difficult.\", \"from\": 39721, \"to\": 39880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"messages\", \"from\": 39742, \"to\": 39750}, {\"ngram\": \"several days\", \"from\": 39755, \"to\": 39767}, {\"ngram\": \"courage\", \"from\": 39809, \"to\": 39816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am just not able to talk \\u2026 [His] people and the BJP have spoiled everything.\", \"from\": 39881, \"to\": 39959, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 39931, \"end\": 39934, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"score\": 0.9999995690261376, \"rank\": 2.2104608770043675e-07, \"text\": \"BJP\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bharatiya_Janata_Party\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 39916, \"to\": 39922}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 39948, \"to\": 39958}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Now whatever I have to say, I will say in court.\\\"\", \"from\": 39960, \"to\": 40009, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"whatever\", \"from\": 39964, \"to\": 39972}, {\"ngram\": \"court\", \"from\": 40002, \"to\": 40007}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But for now, there is a more immediate challenge at hand - the world's biggest sporting stage awaits.\", \"from\": 40011, \"to\": 40112, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a more immediate challenge\", \"from\": 40033, \"to\": 40059}, {\"ngram\": \"hand\", \"from\": 40063, \"to\": 40067}, {\"ngram\": \"the world's biggest sporting stage\", \"from\": 40070, \"to\": 40104}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vinesh Phogat, 29, a feisty, five-feet-two-inch (157cm) wrestler has a smile that can light up a stadium.\", \"from\": 40114, \"to\": 40219, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Vinesh Phogat\", \"from\": 40114, \"to\": 40127}, {\"ngram\": \"(157cm\", \"from\": 40162, \"to\": 40168}, {\"ngram\": \"a smile\", \"from\": 40183, \"to\": 40190}, {\"ngram\": \"a stadium\", \"from\": 40209, \"to\": 40218}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also has many firsts to her credit, and a stock of gold, silver and bronze medals won everywhere from Birmingham to Bishkek, Glasgow to the Gold Coast.\", \"from\": 40220, \"to\": 40375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 40326, \"end\": 40336, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\", \"score\": 0.9997503087590769, \"rank\": 0.00019135642020785232, \"text\": \"Birmingham\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Birmingham\"}, {\"begin\": 40340, \"end\": 40347, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishkek\", \"score\": 0.9999959406437111, \"rank\": 4.059372013838993e-06, \"text\": \"Bishkek\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishkek\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bishkek\"}], \"noun_phrases\