 {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She is ziddi (obstinate) and does not get scared.\", \"from\": 41040, \"to\": 41090, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ziddi (obstinate\", \"from\": 41048, \"to\": 41064}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Once she decides something, she does not think much.\", \"from\": 41091, \"to\": 41143, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 41108, \"to\": 41117}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She just does it,\\\" Somveer Rathi, her husband and a wrestler, said of Vinesh.\", \"from\": 41144, \"to\": 41221, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 41214, \"end\": 41220, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Somveer Rathi\", \"from\": 41163, \"to\": 41176}, {\"ngram\": \"her husband\", \"from\": 41178, \"to\": 41189}, {\"ngram\": \"a wrestler\", \"from\": 41194, \"to\": 41204}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In 2018, when they got married, in addition to the traditional seven vows mandated by Hindu rituals, they took an extra vow: \\\"Beti bachao, beti padhao, beti khilao [Save daughters, teach daughters and let them play].\\\"\", \"from\": 41222, \"to\": 41439, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 41308, \"end\": 41313, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hindus\", \"score\": 0.9976841313926378, \"rank\": 0.0016020178875698764, \"text\": \"Hindu\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hindus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hindus\"}, {\"begin\": 41348, \"end\": 41372, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beti_Bachao_Beti_Padhao\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Beti bachao, beti padhao\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beti_Bachao_Beti_Padhao\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Beti_Bachao_Beti_Padhao