\": 43121}, {\"ngram\": \"[wrestling academies\", \"from\": 43131, \"to\": 43151}, {\"ngram\": \"their wrestlers\", \"from\": 43172, \"to\": 43187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But this time Brij Bhushan's men had threatened that if any girl helps her, becomes her sparring partner, they will destroy their career and finish any akhara that sends girls to train with Vinesh,\\\" a wrestler close to her told Al Jazeera.\", \"from\": 43220, \"to\": 43459, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 43234, \"end\": 43238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Braj\", \"score\": 0.9999999999998863, \"rank\": 1.1195432625044079e-13, \"text\": \"Brij\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Braj\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Braj\"}, {\"begin\": 43410, \"end\": 43416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}, {\"begin\": 43448, \"end\": 43458, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 0.999982858224182, \"rank\": 1.706186779111222e-05, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"any girl\", \"from\": 43276, \"to\": 43284}, {\"ngram\": \"her sparring partner\", \"from\": 43304, \"to\": 43324}, {\"ngram\": \"their career\", \"from\": 43344, \"to\": 43356}, {\"ngram\": \"any akhara\", \"from\": 43368, \"to\": 43378}, {\"ngram\": \"girls\", \"from\": 43390, \"to\": 43395}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But giving up does not cross her mind,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 43461, \"to\": 43510, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her mind\", \"from\": 43491, \"to\": 43499}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So Vinesh wrestled and trained with boys.\", \"from\": 43511, \"to\": 43552, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Vinesh\", \"from\": 43514, \"to\": 43520}, {\"ngram\": \"boys\", \"from\": 43547, \"to\": 43551}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In April this year she qualified for the Olympics, and in July she won gold at Spain's Grand Prix wrestling tournament.\", \"from\": 43554, \"to\": 43673, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 43633, \"end\": 43638, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"score\": 0.8804142000426858, \"rank\": 0.1353393878421001, \"text\": \"Spain\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Spain\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"April\", \"from\": 43557, \"to\": 43562}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 43591, \"to\": 43603}, {\"ngram\": \"July\", \"from\": 43612, \"to\": 43616}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 43625, \"to\": 43629}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Haryana has the dubious distinction of having the highest rate of crime against women in India and the country's lowest gender ratio - 879 females for every 1,000 males.\", \"from\": 43675, \"to\": 43844, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 43675, \"end\": 43682, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4365827962161084e-18, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}, {\"begin\": 43764, \"end\": 43769, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"score\": 0.99999965881358, \"rank\": 2.4266616167827035e-07, \"text\": \"India\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/India\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the dubious distinction\", \"from\": 43687, \"to\": 43710}, {\"ngram\": \"the highest rate\", \"from\": 43721, \"to\": 43737}, {\"ngram\": \"crime\", \"from\": 43741, \"to\": 43746}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 43755, \"to\": 43760}, {\"ngram\": \"the country's lowest gender ratio - 879 females\", \"from\": 43774, \"to\": 43821}, {\"ngram\": \"every 1,000 males\", \"from\": 43826, \"to\": 43843}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But often forgotten in the shocking, gory stories of female foeticide and honour killings is the stubbornness of Haryana's women, their refusal to give up.\", \"from\": 43845, \"to\": 44000, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 43958, \"end\": 43965, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4365827962161084e-18, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the shocking, gory stories\", \"from\": 43868, \"to\": 43894}, {\"ngram\": \"female foeticide\", \"from\": 43898, \"to\": 43914}, {\"ngram\": \"honour killings\", \"from\": 43919, \"to\": 43934}, {\"ngram\": \"the stubbornness\", \"from\": 43938, \"to\": 43954}, {\"ngram\": \"their refusal\", \"from\": 43975, \"to\": 43988}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was visible in the late 1990s, when young girls in singlets stood around mud pits in villages, ignoring abuses and insults, itching to fight for a life beyond marriage and domesticity.\", \"from\": 44002, \"to\": 44189, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the late 1990s\", \"from\": 44020, \"to\": 44034}, {\"ngram\": \"young girls\", \"from\": 44041, \"to\": 44052}, {\"ngram\": \"singlets\", \"from\": 44056, \"to\": 44064}, {\"ngram\": \"mud pits\", \"from\": 44078, \"to\": 44086}, {\"ngram\": \"villages\", \"from\": 44090, \"to\": 44098}, {\"ngram\": \"abuses\", \"from\": 44109, \"to\": 44115}, {\"ngram\": \"insults\", \"from\": 44120, \"to\": 44127}, {\"ngram\": \"a life\", \"from\": 44150, \"to\": 44156}, {\"ngram\": \"marriage\", \"from\": 44164, \"to\": 44172}, {\"ngram\": \"domesticity\", \"from\": 44177, \"to\": 44188}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's in play every time a woman in Haryana defies the diktats of khaps - caste-based village councils - and marries the man she loves.\", \"from\": 44190, \"to\": 44324, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 44225, \"end\": 44232, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.4365827962161084e-18, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"play\", \"from\": 44198, \"to\": 44202}, {\"ngram\": \"a woman\", \"from\": 44214, \"to\": 44221}, {\"ngram\": \"the diktats\", \"from\": 44240, \"to\": 44251}, {\"ngram\": \"khaps - caste-based village councils\", \"from\": 44255, \"to\": 44291}, {\"ngram\": \"the man\", \"from\": 44306, \"to\": 44313}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's also visible on Vinesh's face these days.\", \"from\": 44325, \"to\": 44371, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 44346, \"end\": 44352, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vinesh\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vinesh_Phogat\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Phogat is competing in the 50kg category and will be up against, among others, Japan's Yui Susaki, 25, the defending champion and a daunting legend who has never lost an international match.\", \"from\": 44373, \"to\": 44563, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Phogat\", \"from\": 44373, \"to\": 44379}, {\"ngram\": \"the 50kg category\", \"from\": 44396, \"to\": 44413}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 44444, \"to\": 44450}, {\"ngram\": \"the defending champion\", \"from\": 44476, \"to\": 44498}, {\"ngram\": \"a daunting legend\", \"from\": 44503, \"to\": 44520}, {\"ngram\": \"an international match\", \"from\": 44540, \"to\": 44562}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her regimen these days is to focus on speed and wrestling techniques with an eye on her opponents' strengths and weak points.\", \"from\": 44565, \"to\": 44690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Her regimen\", \"from\": 44565, \"to\": 44576}, {\"ngram\": \"speed and wrestling techniques\", \"from\": 44603, \"to\": 44633}, {\"ngram\": \"an eye\", \"from\": 44639, \"to\": 44645}, {\"ngram\": \"her opponents' strengths\", \"from\": 44649, \"to\": 44673}, {\"ngram\": \"weak points\", \"from\": 44678, \"to\": 44689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has shut out all distractions.\", \"from\": 44692, \"to\": 44726, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all distractions\", \"from\": 44709, \"to\": 44725}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Those days spent on the pavement and being dragged by the police on the streets are in the past.\", \"from\": 44727, \"to\": 44823, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Those days\", \"from\": 44727, \"to\": 44737}, {\"ngram\": \"the pavement\", \"from\": 44747, \"to\": 44759}, {\"ngram\": \"the police\", \"from\": 44781, \"to\": 44791}, {\"ngram\": \"the streets\", \"from\": 44795, \"to\": 44806}, {\"ngram\": \"the past\", \"from\": 44814, \"to\": 44822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The national awards she returned in protest against WFI's allegedly rigged elections are now a fading memory.\", \"from\": 44824, \"to\": 44933, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The national awards\", \"from\": 44824, \"to\": 44843}, {\"ngram\": \"protest\", \"from\": 44860, \"to\": 44867}, {\"ngram\": \"WFI's allegedly rigged elections\", \"from\": 44876, \"to\": 44908}, {\"ngram\": \"a fading memory\", \"from\": 44917, \"to\": 44932}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But sometimes Singh's taunt after her loss at the Tokyo Olympics, when he called her \\\"khota sikka\\\" (counterfeit coin), rankles.\", \"from\": 44935, \"to\": 45062, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Singh's taunt\", \"from\": 44949, \"to\": 44962}, {\"ngram\": \"her loss\", \"from\": 44969, \"to\": 44977}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Olympics\", \"from\": 44981, \"to\": 44999}, {\"ngram\": \"her \\\"khota sikka\", \"from\": 45016, \"to\": 45032}, {\"ngram\": \"counterfeit coin\", \"from\": 45035, \"to\": 45051}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Vinesh lets it stay, lets the rage build up.\", \"from\": 45064, \"to\": 45108, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Vinesh\", \"from\": 45064, \"to\": 45070}, {\"ngram\": \"the rage\", \"from\": 45090, \"to\": 45098}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Then, her teeth press down on her folded lips, her head tilts and her eyes narrow, fixed on the ground in front.\", \"from\": 45109, \"to\": 45221, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her teeth\", \"from\": 45115, \"to\": 45124}, {\"ngram\": \"her folded lips\", \"from\": 45139, \"to\": 45154}, {\"ngram\": \"her head tilts\", \"from\": 45156, \"to\": 45170}, {\"ngram\": \"her eyes\", \"from\": 45175, \"to\": 45183}, {\"ngram\": \"the ground\", \"from\": 45201, \"to\": 45211}, {\"ngram\": \"front\", \"from\": 45215, \"to\": 45220}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She sprints and does manic push-ups, increasing her speed and keeping her heart rate above 190bpm, the rate at which her heart beats during big-game bouts.\", \"from\": 45222, \"to\": 45377, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"manic push-ups\", \"from\": 45243, \"to\": 45257}, {\"ngram\": \"her speed\", \"from\": 45270, \"to\": 45279}, {\"ngram\": \"her heart rate\", \"from\": 45292, \"to\": 45306}, {\"ngram\": \"the rate\", \"from\": 45321, \"to\": 45329}, {\"ngram\": \"her heart\", \"from\": 45339, \"to\": 45348}, {\"ngram\": \"big-game bouts\", \"from\": 45362, \"to\": 45376}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has an Olympic medal to win, and the wrestling dreams of Haryana's young girls to save.\", \"from\": 45379, \"to\": 45470, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 45440, \"end\": 45447, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Haryana\", \"score\": 0.9915447043279092, \"rank\": 0.007119686718214747, \"text\": \"Haryana\", \"types\": [\"Q